		<div id="div-comment-41356" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/594a295adb336c81a4fd7b4b3c1d7c31?s=55&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D55&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-55 photo' height='55' width='55' />		<span class="authorname">Peter Masterson</span>
